<h1>ListComponent</h1>

<h2><code>\{{uic-list}}</code></h2>

<h2>Description</h2>

<p>
  The <code>\{{uic-list}}</code> component can be used to render a list of models or objects.
</p>

{{code-panel name="list-model-example.js"}}

{{code-panel name="list-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-example}}
  {{uic-list model=array}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

<hr>

<h3>tagName</h3>

<p>
  By default the list is rendered into a <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> element.  You can
  easily change that by setting the <code>tagName</code> attribute of the list
  component
</p>

{{code-panel name="ordered-list-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET ordered-list-example}}
  {{uic-list tagName="ol" model=array}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

<hr>

<h3>Template Block</h3>

<p>
  If you want to customise the list item  you can provide a template block to the
  list component.
</p>

{{code-panel name="list-block-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-block-example}}
  {{#uic-list model=array as |item|}}
    ... {{item.name}} ...
  {{/uic-list}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

<hr>

<h3>Class</h3>

<p>There are some built-in class names that can be applied to the list component.</p>

{{uic-list model=builtInClassNames}}

{{code-panel name="list-class-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-class-example}}
  {{uic-list class="default" model=array}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

{{code-panel name="list-inset-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-inset-example}}
  {{uic-list class="inset-border default" model=array}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

<hr>

<h3>selectItem</h3>

<p>
  You can provide an action to the <code>selectItem</code> attribute.  This action
  will be called when a list item is clicked with the list-item as the first argument.
</p>

{{code-panel name="list-select-example.hbs"}}

{{code-panel name="list-select-action-example.js"}}

<h3>List-item Component</h3>

<p>
  You can provide a component to be used for each list item by setting the
  <code>listItemComponent</code> attribute of the list component.
</p>

{{code-panel name="list-item-component-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-item-component-example}}
  {{uic-list listItemComponent="my-custom-list-item" model=array}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>

{{code-panel name="list-item-component-block-example.hbs"}}

<div>
{{! BEGIN-SNIPPET list-item-component-block-example}}
  {{#uic-list listItemComponent="my-custom-list-item" model=array as |item|}}
    {{uic-check-box}} {{item.name}}
  {{/uic-list}}
{{! END-SNIPPET }}
</div>
